Increment version:
iso8583.__init__.__version__

Update change log:
CHANGELOG.rst

Doctest:
python -m doctest .\iso8583\__init__.py
python -m doctest .\iso8583\encoder.py
python -m doctest .\iso8583\decoder.py
python -m doctest .\iso8583\tools.py

Lint:
flake8 iso8583\__init__.py
